and makes no sense.

580
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:31,940
Who writes a report letter like this?

581
00:23:35,590 --> 00:23:37,200
Although the person who wrote this letter

582
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:38,160
doesn't seem to have a

583
00:23:38,160 --> 00:23:39,720
high education background,

584
00:23:39,720 --> 00:23:41,050
their purpose is clear.

585
00:23:41,480 --> 00:23:42,640
Is it possible that

586
00:23:43,750 --> 00:23:45,600
he wrote it under some sort of

587
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:46,970
pressure or fear?

588
00:23:48,240 --> 00:23:50,500
Director Gao, do you have tweezers here?

589
00:24:02,070 --> 00:24:04,480
250174.

590
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:08,330
Could it be an ID number?

591
00:24:10,110 --> 00:24:10,780
If...

592
00:24:10,830 --> 00:24:11,510
Based on these digits—

593
00:24:11,510 --> 00:24:13,200
if they are the first few digits
of an ID number—

594
00:24:13,200 --> 00:24:13,920
the informant is indeed

595
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:14,980
from Sanjiangkou.

596
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:16,230
How did you

597
00:24:16,230 --> 00:24:17,550
mess up the report letter like this?

598
00:24:17,550 --> 00:24:18,400
I didn't mean to.

599
00:24:18,400 --> 00:24:20,400
I didn't know it was a report letter.

600
00:24:21,830 --> 00:24:23,590
When Director Lu had his accident,

601
00:24:23,590 --> 00:24:25,390
you were in Sanjiangkou, right?

602
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:25,880
Yes.

603
00:24:27,110 --> 00:24:28,710
Then how do you explain this?

604
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:30,580
It's fishy.

605
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:32,650
Well...

606
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:33,790
who...

607
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:35,210
is this Director Zhang?

608
00:24:37,750 --> 00:24:38,310
It's me.

609
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:43,200
No matter what the situation is,

610
00:24:43,310 --> 00:24:45,400
the Provincial Department
is going to send someone down

611
00:24:45,400 --> 00:24:47,060
to serve as this deputy chief.

612
00:24:47,880 --> 00:24:49,950
We must investigate Lu Zheng's case

613
00:24:50,110 --> 00:24:51,010
thoroughly,

614
00:24:51,510 --> 00:24:53,370
so that no one has anything to say.

615
00:24:55,720 --> 00:24:56,320
Yan Liang.

616
00:24:58,200 --> 00:25:00,800
I don't have anyone
at this critical juncture.

617
00:25:05,550 --> 00:25:06,200
I thought

618
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:08,590
only goldfish have a 7-second memory.

619
00:25:09,550 --> 00:25:10,460
The last time we robbed,

620
00:25:10,460 --> 00:25:12,190
we were inexperienced.

621
00:25:12,790 --> 00:25:13,650
We got nervous,

622
00:25:13,830 --> 00:25:16,630
didn't notice
the savings office's door opening,

623
00:25:16,720 --> 00:25:18,880
and just focused
on smashing the glass as planned.

624
00:25:18,880 --> 00:25:20,010
We didn't get a dime.

625
00:25:20,640 --> 00:25:22,300
This time I learned my lesson.

626
00:25:23,550 --> 00:25:25,240
After so many days of preparation,

627
00:25:25,240 --> 00:25:26,240
we found the target,

628
00:25:26,240 --> 00:25:28,040
and the robbery was successful.

629
00:25:28,590 --> 00:25:29,640
The shiny gold

630
00:25:29,640 --> 00:25:30,960
is right in front of us.

631
00:25:34,510 --> 00:25:36,040
But I am very disappointed.

632
00:25:36,270 --> 00:25:37,070
Because you

633
00:25:37,310 --> 00:25:39,310
didn't learn your lesson like I did.

634
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:40,000
Why

635
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:41,530
didn't you take more gold?

636
00:25:41,750 --> 00:25:42,680
Why did you stuff

637
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:43,960
a 20-jin statue of the God of Wealth

638
00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:44,790
into your bag?

639
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:45,880
Well, brother, I...

640
00:25:45,880 --> 00:25:47,030
It was placed in the middle,

641
00:25:47,030 --> 00:25:48,680
and I thought it looked quite valuable.

642
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:49,480
It felt

643
00:25:49,790 --> 00:25:50,790
like Hetian jade.

644
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:52,000
Hetian jade?

645
00:25:52,350 --> 00:25:54,480
A 20-jin piece of Hetian jade

646
00:25:54,830 --> 00:25:56,550
in a store the size of a fingernail?

647
00:25:56,550 --> 00:25:58,550
You think it was the Forbidden City?

648
00:25:58,550 --> 00:25:59,240
Well, at least

649
00:25:59,240 --> 00:26:00,880
it's the God of Wealth.

650
00:26:03,830 --> 00:26:04,720
Robbing a gold store

651
00:26:04,720 --> 00:26:06,960
and ending up taking a statue
of the God of Wealth—

652
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:08,560
you're the only one in China.

653
00:26:09,640 --> 00:26:11,110
Come on. What's the big deal?

654
00:26:11,110 --> 00:26:12,730
We can just rob it again.

655
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:14,200
It's just robbery.

656
00:26:14,200 --> 00:26:15,680
What's there to be afraid of?

657
00:26:15,680 --> 00:26:16,720
Heraclitus said,

658
00:26:16,720 --> 00:26:17,480
one cannot step

659
00:26:17,480 --> 00:26:19,000
into the same river twice.

660
00:26:20,260 --> 00:26:21,460
Wait, who is this guy?

661
00:26:21,590 --> 00:26:22,570
We made such a big scene.

662
00:26:22,570 --> 00:26:23,900
Do you dare to rob again?

663
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:27,400
We are risking our lives to make money.

664
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:29,400
If we slip up even slightly,
we'll end up in jail.

665
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:30,800
We can't do this forever.

666
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:32,000
Then what do we do?

667
00:26:40,550 --> 00:26:42,610
Neither of us has any special skills.

668
00:26:42,790 --> 00:26:43,790
Finding a proper job

669
00:26:43,790 --> 00:26:44,650
is impossible.

670
00:26:45,070 --> 00:26:45,960
Doing business—

671
00:26:45,960 --> 00:26:47,690
we're not cut out for it either.

672
00:26:49,240 --> 00:26:50,900
We need to change our mindset.

673
00:26:51,680 --> 00:26:52,550
Let's do something easy

674
00:26:52,550 --> 00:26:54,280
that doesn't require capital.

675
00:26:57,310 --> 00:26:58,310
Work the streets?

676
00:26:59,070 --> 00:27:00,110
Brother, I-I can't do it.

677
00:27:00,110 --> 00:27:01,110
Absolutely not.

678
00:27:01,160 --> 00:27:02,190
I can't do this.

679
00:27:02,400 --> 00:27:03,680
I mean, robbing stores won't work.

680
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:05,080
Let's change direction.

681
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:06,790
Let's rob people.

682
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,330
Trafficking women?

683
00:27:09,550 --> 00:27:10,480
That's too wicked.

684
00:27:10,480 --> 00:27:11,240
I can't do that. I can't do that.

685
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:11,720
I can't.

686
00:27:20,510 --> 00:27:22,500
[Confession from Prison: Lost Ten Millions
but Did Not Dare to Report]

687
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:24,510
Ten million.

688
00:27:25,400 --> 00:27:26,740
How many stores do we have to rob

689
00:27:26,740 --> 00:27:28,560
to make 10 million?

690
00:27:27,370 --> 00:27:32,490
[Sanjiangkou Entertainment Newspaper]

691
00:27:29,480 --> 00:27:31,620
Robbing a corrupt official will do.

692
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:35,240
Hurry up and pack. We're leaving tomorrow.

693
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:35,800
Leave?

694
00:27:35,880 --> 00:27:36,350
Why?

695
00:27:36,920 --> 00:27:38,120
We're not staying here?

696
00:27:38,120 --> 00:27:39,300
Definitely not.

697
00:27:39,720 --> 00:27:40,590
What did that cop

698
00:27:40,590 --> 00:27:41,730
say today?

699
00:27:42,070 --> 00:27:42,960
Alright, don't linger here.

700
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:44,290
It's dangerous. Go now.

701
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:49,160
It's a hint from fate.

702
00:27:52,110 --> 00:27:53,000
Makes sense.

703
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:55,610
So brother, where are we going?

704
00:27:58,310 --> 00:27:59,240
To Sanjiangkou.

705
00:28:00,000 --> 00:28:01,860
Rob a corrupt official, get rich,

706
00:28:02,770 --> 00:28:04,430
and make a name for ourselves.

707
00:28:05,750 --> 00:28:06,030
Brother,

708
00:28:06,030 --> 00:28:07,830
why are we going to Sanjiangkou?

709
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:09,690
Brother,

710
00:28:09,880 --> 00:28:10,550
why?

711
00:28:13,330 --> 00:28:14,620
I just checked.

712
00:28:15,310 --> 00:28:16,310
Sanjiangkou is the only destination

713
00:28:16,310 --> 00:28:17,440
with 2 tickets left.

714
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:23,450
It's all arranged

715
00:28:23,510 --> 00:28:25,160
by Heaven.

716
00:28:28,160 --> 00:28:28,960
Zhang Yi'ang.

717
00:28:29,350 --> 00:28:29,950
Come here.

718
00:28:35,030 --> 00:28:36,830
The Party Committee has decided

719
00:28:37,160 --> 00:28:38,290
that you will be sent

720
00:28:39,590 --> 00:28:40,520
to Sanjiangkou.

721
00:28:41,790 --> 00:28:42,960
I'm not from the CID.

722
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:44,760
Can CID still spare someone?

723
00:28:46,960 --> 00:28:48,690
It's not that I don't want to go.

724
00:28:48,830 --> 00:28:50,310
I've just got a gout flare-up recently.

725
00:28:50,310 --> 00:28:51,040
I can't walk.

726
00:28:51,110 --> 00:28:52,510
How did you get in just now?

727
00:28:52,510 --> 00:28:53,480
Did you crawl in?

728
00:28:59,350 --> 00:29:00,150
Zhang Yi'ang.

729
00:29:04,110 --> 00:29:04,910
How many cases

730
00:29:05,550 --> 00:29:06,880
have you solved with me?

731
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:08,090
Do you remember?

732
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:11,380
You don't remember at all.

733
00:29:12,350 --> 00:29:13,030
I do.

734
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:16,680
From...

735
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:19,860
the serial murders on Fengqi Road

736
00:29:20,440 --> 00:29:22,070
to the White Elephant case we solved

737
00:29:22,070 --> 00:29:24,030
just before I was promoted
to deputy director—

738
00:29:24,030 --> 00:29:24,830
17 major cases

739
00:29:25,550 --> 00:29:26,200
in total.

740
00:29:30,110 --> 00:29:31,370
What does that tell us?

741
00:29:33,110 --> 00:29:34,070
It tells us

742
00:29:34,070 --> 00:29:35,930
your ability is beyond question,

743
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:38,610
your political reliability is solid,

744
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:40,080
and you're a fighter.

745
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:44,030
You need to get back on your feet.

746
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:46,830
Look at me!

747
00:29:49,000 --> 00:29:51,800
Yan Liang came to the bureau
at the same time as you.

748
00:29:52,510 --> 00:29:53,590
Look at him now.

749
00:29:53,640 --> 00:29:54,840
Now look at yourself.

750
00:29:55,830 --> 00:29:57,830
Do you even have friends left in CID?

751
00:29:58,440 --> 00:29:59,040
Or rather,

752
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:00,160
Is there anyone in the CID

753
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:01,640
who still considers you a friend?

754
00:30:01,640 --> 00:30:02,030
Yes.

755
00:30:04,070 --> 00:30:05,480
What accompanies me in my loneliness...

756
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:06,480
is my loneliness.

757
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:08,720
You can't go on like this.

758
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:09,980
You'll ruin yourself.

759
00:30:09,980 --> 00:30:10,780
You know that?

760
00:30:20,240 --> 00:30:21,040
Zhang Yi'ang.

761
00:30:23,480 --> 00:30:24,400
Wasn't it just that incident 5 years ago,

762
00:30:24,400 --> 00:30:25,400
when the murderer jumped off a building,

763
00:30:25,400 --> 00:30:26,730
that affected you a bit?

764
00:30:27,680 --> 00:30:28,880
You can't get over it?

765
00:30:30,030 --> 00:30:31,830
What's that saying in football?

766
00:30:34,680 --> 00:30:35,080
Right.

767
00:30:35,350 --> 00:30:36,550
As an athlete,

768
00:30:36,590 --> 00:30:37,720
instead of playing,

769
00:30:37,830 --> 00:30:40,030
you just sit on the bench doing nothing?

770
00:30:40,750 --> 00:30:42,480
And you have the nerve to laugh?

771
00:30:42,680 --> 00:30:44,030
If I wasn't wearing this uniform,

772
00:30:44,030 --> 00:30:45,110
I'd smack you.

773
00:30:52,440 --> 00:30:53,370
I'm telling you.

774
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:55,840
This is your last chance.

775
00:30:57,480 --> 00:30:58,540
Go to Sanjiangkou,

776
00:30:58,920 --> 00:31:00,350
take a temporary post
at the municipal bureau.

777
00:31:00,350 --> 00:31:01,030
investigate the case

778
00:31:01,030 --> 00:31:02,200
thoroughly,

779
00:31:02,540 --> 00:31:04,110
and close it cleanly.

780
00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:06,520
At most a year.

781
00:31:06,960 --> 00:31:08,440
I'll transfer you back within a year,

782
00:31:08,440 --> 00:31:10,160
and you'll be entrusted
with an important position.

783
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:11,310
I have to go for a year?

784
00:31:11,310 --> 00:31:11,840
One year.

785
00:31:12,070 --> 00:31:13,240
Complete the mission,

786
00:31:13,240 --> 00:31:14,640
and don't cause trouble.

787
00:31:15,030 --> 00:31:15,830
Director Gao,

788
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:19,080
do I have to go?

789
00:31:19,110 --> 00:31:19,720
Yes.

790
00:31:21,680 --> 00:31:22,790
Take Li Qian with you

791
00:31:22,790 --> 00:31:24,450
to Sanjiangkou to assist you.

792
00:31:25,790 --> 00:31:27,240
What mistake did she make?

793
00:31:27,240 --> 00:31:28,970
You think everyone is like you?

794
00:31:29,510 --> 00:31:31,040
That girl is very talented.

795
00:31:31,750 --> 00:31:33,680
The department plans
to make an exception and promote her.

796
00:31:33,680 --> 00:31:35,280
She needs a year of training.

797
00:31:35,450 --> 00:31:36,820
Keep an eye on her.

798
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:38,110
Don't let anything happen to her.

799
00:31:38,110 --> 00:31:38,680
Got it?

800
00:31:44,200 --> 00:31:44,840
Go.

801
00:31:54,480 --> 00:31:55,280
What's wrong?

802
00:31:55,310 --> 00:31:56,030
Do you have something to say?

803
00:31:56,030 --> 00:31:57,000
No, I don't.

804
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:58,310
Come back.

805
00:31:58,960 --> 00:31:59,720
Say what you want to say.

806
00:31:59,720 --> 00:32:00,650
Don't hold it in.

807
00:32:02,110 --> 00:32:02,960
I just feel

808
00:32:03,310 --> 00:32:04,310
this arrangement

809
00:32:05,440 --> 00:32:06,210
reminds me of

810
00:32:06,240 --> 00:32:06,920
a poem by Pushkin.

811
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:07,880
I beg you,

812
00:32:08,110 --> 00:32:08,970
please,

813
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:09,930
shut your mouth.

814
00:32:10,030 --> 00:32:11,000
If you recite poetry to me again,

815
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:11,530
I will...

816
00:32:11,590 --> 00:32:13,000
Hurry up and get to Sanjiangkou!

817
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:15,260
Don't come back until you close the case!

818
00:32:17,350 --> 00:32:18,640
I won't say too much.

819
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:21,010
I'll wait for your triumphant return.

820
00:32:24,000 --> 00:32:25,200
Show what you've got.

821
00:32:25,350 --> 00:32:27,080
Let me see the old Zhang Yi'ang.

822
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:32,600
Stay safe.

823
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:41,480
Mentor.

824
00:32:41,750 --> 00:32:42,550
Get in the car!

825
00:32:45,300 --> 00:32:49,320
[Ping'an Province
National Safety Department]

826
00:32:50,160 --> 00:32:52,360
If life deceives you,

827
00:32:52,500 --> 00:32:53,660
don't be sad,

828
00:32:53,920 --> 00:32:54,920
don't be anxious.

829
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:57,390
[Ping'an Province
National Safety Department]

830
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:57,070
You need to stay calm in melancholy days.

831
00:32:57,070 --> 00:32:58,070
Happy days

832
00:32:58,590 --> 00:32:59,850
will eventually come!

833
00:33:38,350 --> 00:33:38,880
Brother,

834
00:33:39,440 --> 00:33:40,350
do you think this person will agree

835
00:33:40,350 --> 00:33:41,220
to change seats with me?

836
00:33:41,220 --> 00:33:42,420
I want to sit with you.

837
00:33:45,850 --> 00:33:48,250
Brother, you really know
how to enjoy life.

838
00:33:49,510 --> 00:33:51,240
Not only do I know how to enjoy life,

839
00:33:51,240 --> 00:33:52,840
but I also value friendship.

840
00:33:53,550 --> 00:33:54,550
Thanks, brother.

841
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:01,410
Brother.

842
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:02,770
Brother.

843
00:34:03,480 --> 00:34:04,010
Brother.

844
00:34:17,400 --> 00:34:18,150
Let's fight them.

845
00:34:18,150 --> 00:34:18,880
Yeah, right.

846
00:34:18,960 --> 00:34:19,489
Let's go.

847
00:34:30,550 --> 00:34:31,070
Here.

848
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:02,710
Having you,

849
00:35:02,760 --> 00:35:05,110
a promising talent
from the Provincial Department,

850
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:06,150
come with me—

851
00:35:07,880 --> 00:35:08,960
whatever happens in the future,

852
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:10,890
I want to apologize in advance now.

853
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:17,040
[Harmony]

854
00:35:37,430 --> 00:35:37,830
I...

855
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:38,840
really haven't handled a case

856
00:35:38,840 --> 00:35:40,170
in many years.

857
00:35:40,510 --> 00:35:41,570
So I have to read it.

858
00:35:41,590 --> 00:35:44,360
Reviewing the past
helps understand the present.

859
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:46,420
You carry a theory textbook with you.

860
00:35:47,230 --> 00:35:48,710
You are always prepared.

861
00:35:49,550 --> 00:35:50,800
You must have taken a lot of notes.

862
00:35:50,720 --> 00:35:50,920
[Index]

863
00:35:51,010 --> 00:35:52,000
[Retail]

864
00:35:53,930 --> 00:35:54,880
[Retail]

865
00:35:55,300 --> 00:35:55,780
[Criminal Psychology]

866
00:35:55,480 --> 00:35:57,030
This is a new edition.

867
00:35:57,060 --> 00:35:58,030
